Un delincuente profesional atrapado por las autoridades mexicanas es internado en una dura prisión donde aprende a sobrevivir con la ayuda de un niño.
Al tiempo que el mayor robo de diamantes es puesto en marcha, un psicólogo policial intentan convencer a un expresidiario de que no salte de una azotea.
A young star at a Wall Street firm finds that the white-collar world is filled with as much crime and death as the dangerous hood where he was raised.

While battling the Nottingham Sheriff, Robin Hood and his band of merry men are slain. Distraught over these horrific turn of events Marian and Little John attempt to resurrect Robin and his comrades with disastrous results.
Three childhood friends from Belgrade, Serbia see their destinies change as they become adults during the wartime 1990s.
Three years later, JW gets out of prison, but soon finds himself between the contending parties of his criminal past.
Un equipo de élite de marines se embarca en una misión secreta para recuperar a un agente de la CIA secuestrado.

A un hombre condenado erróneamente por conspiración y espionaje contra los EE. UU. se le ofrece la libertad si puede rescatar a la hija del presidente de una prisión del espacio exterior tomada por reclusos violentos.
Dos operativos de la CIA se enfrentan cuando descubren que han estado saliendo con la misma mujer.
Un agente del servicio secreto británico se enfrenta a la misión de perseguir y eliminar a un terrorista suicida nacido en Gran Bretaña y a su célula terrorista.

Stephanie Plum, desempleada y recién divorciada, consigue un trabajo en el negocio de fianzas de su primo, donde su primera misión la pone tras la pista de un policía local buscado, de su pasado romántico.
A un joven agente de la CIA se le encarga la vigilancia de un fugitivo en un lugar seguro. Pero cuando el sitio es atacado, huyen juntos para intentar acabar con sus enemigos.
Abraham Lincoln, 16º presidente de los Estados Unidos, descubre que los vampiros planean tomar el país y se propone destruirlos.

The story of four high school boys whose undefeated basketball season and friendship are threatened after a drive-by shooting leaves one of them in a coma and one of them with a secret. Brent Fencett, Jed Bracken, and T.J. Lewis are star players on the Charlevoix High School Basketball team; Jackson Carlson is their most obnoxious fan. They are unbeaten on the court a... Leer todo
Creedores de maría Ben y Chon se enfrentan al cartel mexicano que ha secuestrado a la novia que comparten.
The story of Paan Singh Tomar, an Indian athlete and seven-time national steeplechase champion who becomes one of the most feared dacoits in Chambal Valley after his retirement.

When college students sign up for what seems a simple paid research study, they soon realize their lives are in danger. Unfortunately they've unknowingly volunteered their bodies as human collateral in an ongoing U.S. Military experiment.
Jason Mackenzie, a lightning powered vigilante, is called into action when an ancient Scottish creature, The Caillech, returns to our world and plans to destroy it in three days.
Four punks flee the city after a night of violence. Seeking refuge in the Arizona desert, they will find that their friendships can only stretch so far.

Humanity has survived what seemed to be the apocalypse, but a threat still remains. Delta Zulu follows Clark, a freelance reporter who will be amongst the few civilians ever allowed into a Red Zone, a lawless quarantined area that still breathes war. Un exagente de la CIA y su hija distanciada se ven obligados a huir cuando sus empleadores borran todos los registros de su existencia, y los marcan para eliminarlos como parte de una conspiración internacional de gran alcance.
Perseo se enfrenta al traicionero inframundo para rescatar a su padre, Zeus, capturado por su hijo, Ares, y su hermano Hades, que desatan a los antiguos titanes sobre el mundo.
Un profesor de instituto quiere convertirse en luchador de artes marciales para recaudar dinero que permita al colegio seguir ofreciendo actividades extracurriculares.
A clown doll possessed by a demon goes on a bloody rampage of murder after being found and taken into a home.

Amidst the backdrop of the economic downturn, Mike Malone is suddenly laid off from his job of 16 years. In an act of desperation he gets involved in a drug scheme with a young boxer and a petty thief. They manage to pull off a heist and Mike makes a clean getaway. A young California surfer has to grow up in a hurry when he is thrown into a Peruvian political prison in 1980.
Serena, a young girl trained as a killer for hire, teams up with an underground renegade group when she is contracted to stop a hired gun from assassinating a high profile target.

Mei, una niña cuya memoria guarda un valioso código, se ve perseguida por las triadas, la mafia rusa y policías corruptos de Nueva York. En su ayuda acude un antiguo luchador, cuya vida fue destruida por los mafiosos que buscan a Mai.
Un antiguo ladrón busca frenéticamente a su hija desaparecida, que ha sido secuestrada y encerrada en el maletero de un taxi.

John intenta acabar con Luc Deveraux después de que un allanamiento cobra la vida de su mujer y su hija. La lucha enfrenta a John con Andrew Scott y un ejército; mientras tanto, debe enfrentarse a un UniSol en una búsqueda implacable.

column5: Bigwigs, thugs, moguls and mugs, all they want is the silver case.
When a Bolivian drug lord and his family get gunned down by a group of Russian drug runners, it's up to a pair of tough DEA agents to bring them to justice.
Wealthy thrill-seekers pay huge premiums to have themselves inserted into military adventures, only this time things don't go exactly to plan.

When a school bus accident devastates an inner city Los Angeles neighborhood, it will forever change the paths for all. Friendships will be challenged, beliefs questioned and it become a time when they must choose which way to fall.

Three unlikely allies must team up to save humanity when the portal to hell is opened and the undead begin to walk the earth. The group races to find an artifact of great power to close the portal before all hope is lost.
Un estudiante universitario se ve envuelto en el salvaje estilo de vida del motocross profesional de estilo libre.

The martial arts sensation, Shuny Bee, strikes the city of Kathmandu as the Gorkha Protector, to stop the human trafficking of young innocent girls. Although it is a fiction movie, it is based on what is happening in real life situations for a long time in country of Nepal. A reluctant samurai with a dark past sets off on a mission to fulfill his destiny.

Memorial Day, 1993. When 13-year-old Kyle Vogel discovers the World War II footlocker belonging to his grandfather, Bud, everyone tells Kyle to put it back. Luckily, he ignores them. When werewolf Mickey is accidentally killed in a strip club, the girls who work there have until the next full moon before his bloodthirsty wolf pack seek murderous retribution.

Tres jóvenes se ven expuestos a una misteriosa sustancia en el bosque, y como resultado, empiezan a desarrollar increíbles poderes. Trabajarán juntos como diversión para pulir sus habilidades, hasta que una serie de problemas personales los empezarán a poner unos contra otros.

The painful and humorous journey of a selfish athlete who is now down on his luck unable even to keep his job as a bike messenger. He finds a way to redeem his life through the support of friends and by learning that to break from the large group of bikers, the peloton, the winning cyclist must first work with the team.
To avenge his past, Aakash Rana plants a bomb in a train endangering the lives of 500 passengers.
